data.description: Conveniently located to town amenities with an oversized garage that can fit 2 standard trucks.  Easy turn-around driveway, and RV parking available on both sides of the home.  This gives you plenty of space between the houses.  The large windows in the main living area provide you with lots of natural light and a view across the valley.  Kitchen is wide and open to dining area with plenty of space to expand your seating area for large gatherings.  Each of the bedrooms are spacious enough for king or queen bed sets.  Nice sized backyard with block wall.  Plus NO HOA.  Call today for your appointment to tour this home.
